<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l5">ſölıchs alts <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex>s</expan> vnd <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> gewonheıt / daʒ eẅr <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd kawffleẅt bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l6">vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> ʒollfrey / vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd kawffleẅt bey eẅch ʒu Ach . auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l7">ʒollfrey ſein vnd <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> <expan>ſüll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> getan vnd erynnert habt / wıe dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l8">recht / dıe dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Jerlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bey eẅch 
<del rend="strikethrough"><gap reason="illegible"/></del> ſchuldıg ſein <expan>ʒugeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / etlıche Jare </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l9">niht geraicht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> . nach lawt der <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> eẅrs briefs in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l10"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>nehſte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> eẅch geſandt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> / <expan>Hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır mıt den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beſtellet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l11">ſölıche ergangne recht bey eẅch ʒu <expan>raıche<ex>n</ex></expan> . als Jr das vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> in dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l12"><expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> brıef wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> habt Alſo tun wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l13">daʒ vns <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geſworn<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒollner geſagt hat / daʒ dıe rechte dıe dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>Jerl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l14">bey vns ſchuldıg ſein <expan>ʒugeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / auch ettlıche Jare niht geraıcht <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l15">ſo ıſt vns auch von den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fürbracht / wıe ſıe von den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> . vmb ʒölle </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l16">bey eẅch <expan>ʒugeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> angelangt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / daʒ vns nach <expan>ſölıche<ex>m</ex></expan> altem <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l17">frömd nymbt / vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> doch <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ es <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> von den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l18"><expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> niht <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſülle / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleıſſ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l19">mıt den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>ʒubeſtell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / ſölıche ergangne <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſeſſne</expan> recht bey vns ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l20"><expan>raıche<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd / daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> kawffleẅt vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vordru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l21">ʒölle bey eẅch ʒu <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürbas <expan>erlaſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> . vnd ob ſıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ıcht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>bürgt</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l22"><expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> ledıg geſagt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . Da mıt ſıe bey dem <expan>vorgeſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> altem <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l23"><expan>beleıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> . geleıch eẅr <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> kawffleẅt vnd dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l25">ʒollfrey ſein vnd <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / Denn 
<add><ab facs="#facs_130_line_1577033568761_1949">wo </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_line_1577033588888_1965"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc Vnd lat vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> eẅr freẅntlıch <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_130_r2l29">antwurt <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> bey dıſem <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
